# Trinity Design System - Code Owners
# 
# These owners will be automatically requested for review when someone opens
# a pull request that modifies code they own.
#
# Order matters: later patterns take precedence over earlier ones.
# @see https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# DEFAULT OWNERS
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Default: Core maintainers own everything not explicitly assigned
