# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# NOTES
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# Team aliases (create these in GitHub org settings):
#   @trinity/design-system-leads  - Design System Lead + Senior Maintainers
#   @trinity/design-system-core   - Core maintainers (2-3 people)
#   @trinity/design-system-docs   - Documentation team
#   @trinity/ai-team              - AI feature specialists
#   @trinity/data-viz-team        - Data visualization specialists
#   @trinity/data-team            - Data/table specialists
#   @trinity/a11y-champions       - Accessibility advocates
#
# To request review from a team, the team must have read access to the repo.
